{"tid":2378341,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"海鮮意粉蜆殼無肉塞滿飯粒 餐廳老闆：用生命保證不是廚餘","createTime":"2021-01-24T11:36:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-24T12:04:13.000Z","uid":66271,"like":7,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6137cd8644a5bc0adc69f163ef3995538cd01262","tid":2378341,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T11:36:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2855000/2859947/Whats_1024.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2855000%2F2859947%2FWhats_1024.jpeg&h=3231ac72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n台灣一名兩孩之母投訴，指日前到一間西餐廳享用蜆肉意大利粉，期間發現其中一隻蜆殼內藏滿飯粒又沒有蜆肉，質疑是廚餘並向職員反映，職員先估計是廚具未洗乾淨所致，餐廳老闆事後卻有另一番解說，且明言「可以用生命保證不是廚餘」。<br />\n<br />\n一名女網民周三（20日）在Facebook群組「爆怨公社」中發文，表示當天中午接2名孩子放學後，順便在學校附近一間西餐廳吃午飯。事主當時點了一碟蜆肉意粉，沒想到其中一隻蜆殼內竟塞滿飯粒而沒有蜆肉，令她大感疑惑，形容：<br />\n<br />\n「點的是意大利麵，麵裡的蛤蜊（蜆）裡面居然包了整個飯。」<br />\n<br />\n事主馬上向餐廳職員反映情況，對方表示「可能是鍋子沒洗乾淨」。事主直言無法接受解釋，認為「鍋子沒洗乾淨」跟「整顆蛤蜊裝滿飯」沒有關係，甚至質疑蜆肉為餐廳廚餘，她表示：<br />\n<br />\n「5顆蛤蜊裡有2顆沒開，1顆是裝滿滿的飯，真的越想越反胃，店家竟然連一句道歉都沒（有），真的傻眼（無奈）。」<br />\n餐廳老闆：用生命保證不是廚餘<br />\n<br />\n離開餐廳後，事主補充，指餐廳老闆有致電向她解釋，稱因廚師為上一位客人製作燉飯時誤用上太多蜆，故此把蜆從燉飯中「撈出來」，再放在事主的意粉上，堅稱「可以用生命保證不是廚餘」，並指如事主仍有懷疑，可讓她查看閉路電視片段。然而，從事主分享的影片可見，閉路電視鏡頭只看到職員捧餐情況，而未能拍攝廚師烹調過程。<br />\n<br />\n不少網民其後發現該餐廳一向負評如潮，表示不接受老闆解釋，亦有人揶揄事主「有飯有麵」實屬「賺到」："},{"pid":"862f36295bad8cc0cfef1d6a8b80cace8a36be48","tid":2378341,"uid":51346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T11:40:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5826c92fd5ae60d5fe10df1984872672fad226ad","tid":2378341,"uid":40499,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T11:41:42.000Z","msg":"其實係白色珍珠黎"},{"pid":"d2217d47c23fe9fddfe0f7ac308f8dd3e350bbb2","tid":2378341,"uid":133763,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T11:43:36.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">稱因廚師為上一位客人製作燉飯時誤用上太多蜆，故此把蜆從燉飯中「撈出來」，再放在事主的意粉上，堅稱「可以用生命保證不是廚餘」</span><br />\n隻蜆都幾有生命力,食咁多飯<br />\n真係生命保證<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99d1afc03a9459c1f39694c04aecea1d849a63df","tid":2378341,"uid":131884,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T11:43:49.000Z","msg":"邊個職員咁倒米直接話未洗乾淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7837934a041daaef8ad5896e2a2b32d5b091ffb8","tid":2378341,"uid":15954,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99d1afc03a9459c1f39694c04aecea1d849a63df","tid":2378341,"uid":131884,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T11:43:49.000Z","msg":"邊個職員咁倒米直接話未洗乾淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T11:46:32.000Z","msg":"人工低咪倒你米"},{"pid":"50a70cc09942abe8015d09696a4b36f67ff8571e","tid":2378341,"uid":144541,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T11:47:44.000Z","msg":"支那狗扮台灣人搞抹黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"548427be0db7ec93a7b4333383d0d1060479d939","tid":2378341,"uid":112748,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6137cd8644a5bc0adc69f163ef3995538cd01262","tid":2378341,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T11:36:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2855000/2859947/Whats_1024.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.